text: Terrance Hinds is a Trinidadian cricketer. He made his Twenty20 debut for Trinbago Knight Riders in the 2018 Caribbean Premier League on 7 September 2018. He made his first-class debut on 9 January 2020, for Trinidad and Tobago in the first round of the 2019–20 West Indies Championship. In the next round of matches, he scored his maiden century in first-class cricket, with an unbeaten 102 runs. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1990s births Category:Living people Category:Trinidad and Tobago cricketers Category:Trinbago Knight Riders cricketers Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
